titre: EBike Display SW102T LCD Screen Display 0-5 levels for BAFANG BBS01B BBS02B BBSHD Mid Motor Ebike Computer with PAS UART Protoco
titre_da_auto: EBike-display SW102T LCD-skærm 0-5 niveauer til BAFANG BBS01B BBS02B BBSHD midtermotor elcykelcomputer med PAS UART-protokol
description:
Features

The EBike Display SW102T is a comprehensive LCD screen display designed specifically for BAFANG mid-drive electric bike motors, including the BBS01B, BBS02B, and BBSHD models. This user-friendly display provides essential information about your ride, allowing you to monitor and adjust your eBike's performance with ease.

  • Integrated 5-Level PAS (Pedal Assist Sensor) Control: Fine-tune your level of assistance with five distinct PAS settings, ranging from subtle support to powerful boost.
  • Bright LCD Screen: Enjoy clear visibility even in challenging lighting conditions with the bright and easily readable LCD display.
  • UART Protocol Compatibility: The SW102T seamlessly integrates with BAFANG motors via the UART protocol, ensuring reliable data transfer and communication.
  • Intuitive User Interface: Navigate through menus and settings effortlessly with the straightforward and intuitive user interface.

Specifications

The SW102T LCD display is crafted to meet the demanding requirements of eBike systems.

  • Display Type: LCD
  • Screen Size: Compact and easy-to-view
  • PAS Levels: 5 adjustable levels
  • Connectivity: UART Protocol for seamless communication with BAFANG motors
  • Mounting Options: Designed for secure mounting on your eBike handlebar.

Benefits

The EBike Display SW102T offers a multitude of benefits to enhance your eBike riding experience:

  • Personalized Ride Control: Tailor your eBike's power output to match your desired level of assistance, whether you prefer gentle support or powerful acceleration.
  • Enhanced Safety and Visibility: The bright LCD screen ensures easy readability in various lighting conditions, allowing for greater situational awareness during your rides.
  • Seamless Integration: The SW102T seamlessly integrates with BAFANG motors through the UART protocol, ensuring smooth data exchange and reliable performance.
  • User-Friendly Operation: The intuitive user interface makes navigating menus and settings a breeze, allowing for quick and effortless adjustments.

Usage

The SW102T is designed to be easily integrated into your BAFANG-powered eBike. Simply mount the display securely on your handlebars and connect it to your motor using the provided UART cable. Use the intuitive buttons on the display to cycle through menus, adjust PAS levels, and monitor essential riding information such as speed, battery level, and distance.

Regularly check your eBike's battery level and ensure proper charging to optimize performance. Consult the user manual for detailed instructions and safety guidelines specific to your BAFANG motor system.
description_da_auto:
Funktioner

EBike Display SW102T er en omfattende LCD-skærm, der er specielt designet til BAFANG mid-drive elektriske cykelmotorer, herunder BBS01B-, BBS02B- og BBSHD-modellerne. Dette brugervenlige display giver vigtige oplysninger om din tur, så du nemt kan overvåge og justere din elcykels ydeevne.

  • Integreret 5-niveau PAS (Pedal Assist Sensor) kontrol: Finjuster dit assistanceniveau med fem forskellige PAS-indstillinger, lige fra diskret support til kraftig boost.
  • Lys LCD-skærm: Nyd klar synlighed selv under udfordrende lysforhold med det lysstærke og letlæselige LCD-display.
  • UART-protokolkompatibilitet: SW102T integreres problemfrit med BAFANG-motorer via UART-protokollen, hvilket sikrer pålidelig dataoverførsel og kommunikation.
  • Intuitiv brugergrænseflade: Naviger ubesværet gennem menuer og indstillinger med den ligefremme og intuitive brugergrænseflade.

Specifikationer

SW102T LCD-displayet er designet til at opfylde de krævende krav til elcykelsystemer.

  • Skærmtype: LCD
  • Skærmstørrelse: Kompakt og let at se
  • PAS-niveauer: 5 justerbare niveauer
  • Forbindelse: UART-protokol til problemfri kommunikation med BAFANG-motorer
  • Monteringsmuligheder: Designet til sikker montering på dit elcykelstyr.

Fordele

EBike-displayet SW102T tilbyder en lang række fordele, der forbedrer din elcykeloplevelse:

  • Personlig kørekontrol: Tilpas din elcykels effekt, så den matcher dit ønskede niveau af assistance, uanset om du foretrækker blid støtte eller kraftig acceleration.
  • Forbedret sikkerhed og synlighed: Den klare LCD-skærm sikrer nem læsbarhed under forskellige lysforhold, hvilket giver større situationsbevidsthed under dine ture.
  • Problemfri integration: SW102T integreres problemfrit med BAFANG-motorer via UART-protokollen, hvilket sikrer problemfri dataudveksling og pålidelig ydeevne.
  • Brugervenlig betjening: Den intuitive brugergrænseflade gør det nemt at navigere i menuer og indstillinger og muliggør hurtige og nemme justeringer.

Brug

SW102T er designet til nemt at blive integreret i din BAFANG-drevne elcykel. Du skal blot montere displayet sikkert på styret og tilslutte det til din motor ved hjælp af det medfølgende UART-kabel. Brug de intuitive knapper på displayet til at gennemgå menuer, justere PAS-niveauer og overvåge vigtige køreoplysninger såsom hastighed, batteriniveau og distance.

Kontroller regelmæssigt din elcykels batteriniveau og sørg for korrekt opladning for at optimere ydeevnen. Se brugermanualen for detaljerede instruktioner og sikkerhedsretningslinjer, der er specifikke for dit BAFANG-motorsystem.

titre: Bafang 750W 500W kit complet Mid Drive Motor BBS02B Bicycle Electric eBike Conversion Kit Powerful Central e-Bike Engine UART
titre_da_auto: Bafang 750W 500W komplet sæt midterdrevsmotor BBS02B cykel elektrisk elcykel konverteringssæt kraftfuld central elcykelmotor UART
description:
Features

The Bafang BBS02B is a powerful mid-drive electric bike conversion kit designed to transform your bicycle into a capable e-bike. This robust system boasts a 750W peak power output, providing exhilarating acceleration and impressive hill-climbing ability. With its central motor placement, it offers optimal weight distribution and natural pedaling feel.

  • 750W Peak Power Output: Experience effortless acceleration and conquer steep inclines with ease.
  • Mid-Drive Motor Placement:
    • Achieve balanced weight distribution and a natural cycling experience.
  • UART Communication Protocol:
    • Enables seamless integration with compatible displays and accessories for customized control and data monitoring.

Specifications

The Bafang BBS02B is engineered for performance and reliability. Here are some key specifications:

  • Motor Type:
    • Brushless DC (BLDC)
  • Power Output:
    • 750W Peak, 500W Continuous
  • Voltage:
    • 36V or 48V (depending on battery compatibility)
  • Torque:
    • High torque for excellent climbing performance.
  • Pedal Assist Levels:
    • Multiple levels to customize assistance intensity.

Benefits

This electric bike conversion kit offers a range of benefits for riders seeking enhanced cycling capabilities and convenience:

  • Effortless Riding:
    • Enjoy easier commutes, longer rides, and less fatigue with the power assistance provided by the motor.
  • Increased Performance:
    • Conquer hills with confidence and accelerate quickly for a more exhilarating riding experience.
  • Eco-Friendly Option:
    • Reduce your carbon footprint by opting for an electric bike over gasoline-powered vehicles.

Usage

The Bafang BBS02B is designed to be integrated into various bicycle frames. Installation typically involves mounting the motor onto the bottom bracket, connecting the wiring harness, and configuring the display unit.

Once installed, users can select their desired pedal assist level using the controller or display. The motor will then provide assistance proportional to your pedaling effort, making it ideal for a wide range of riding conditions and terrains.
description_da_auto:
Funktioner

Bafang BBS02B er et kraftfuldt konverteringssæt til elcykel med midterdrev, der er designet til at forvandle din cykel til en kapabel elcykel. Dette robuste system kan prale af en peak-effekt på 750 W, hvilket giver spændende acceleration og imponerende bakkekørsel. Med sin centrale placering af motoren tilbyder den optimal vægtfordeling og en naturlig pedalfølelse.

  • 750 W peak-effekt: Oplev ubesværet acceleration og overvind stejle stigninger med lethed.
  • Placering af midterdrevsmotor:
    • Opnå en afbalanceret vægtfordeling og en naturlig cykeloplevelse.
  • UART-kommunikationsprotokol:
    • Muliggør problemfri integration med kompatible displays og tilbehør til tilpasset kontrol og dataovervågning.

Specifikationer

Bafang BBS02B er konstrueret til ydeevne og pålidelighed. Her er nogle vigtige specifikationer:

  • Motortype:
    • Børsteløs DC (BLDC)
  • Effekt:
    • 750W Peak, 500W Kontinuerlig
  • Spænding:
    • 36V eller 48V (afhængigt af batteriets kompatibilitet)
  • Moment:
    • Højt moment for fremragende klatrepræstation.
  • Pedalhjælpsniveauer:
    • Flere niveauer for at tilpasse assistanceintensiteten.

Fordele

Dette elcykelkonverteringssæt tilbyder en række fordele for ryttere, der søger forbedrede cykelfunktioner og bekvemmelighed:

  • Ubesværet kørsel:
    • Nyd lettere pendling, længere ture og mindre træthed med den kraftassistance, som motoren leverer.
  • Øget ydeevne:
    • Bekør bakker med selvtillid og accelerer hurtigt for en mere spændende køreoplevelse.
  • Miljøvenlig mulighed:
    • Reducer dit CO2-aftryk ved at vælge en elcykel frem for benzindrevne køretøjer.

Brug

Bafang BBS02B er designet til at blive integreret i forskellige cykelstel. Installation involverer typisk montering af motoren på krankboksen, tilslutning af ledningsnettet og konfiguration af displayenheden.

Når den er installeret, kan brugerne vælge deres ønskede pedalassistanceniveau ved hjælp af controlleren eller displayet. Motoren vil derefter yde assistance proportionalt med din pedalindsats, hvilket gør den ideel til en bred vifte af køreforhold og terræner.

titre: Ebike Hydraulic Brake Sensor Cable for Bafang BBS01 BBS02 BBSHD Motor Power Cut Off Brake Sensor Electric Bike Accessories
titre_da_auto: Ebike hydraulisk bremsesensorkabel til Bafang BBS01 BBS02 BBSHD motor strømafbryder bremsesensor elektrisk cykeltilbehør
description:
Features

This Ebike Hydraulic Brake Sensor Cable is specifically designed to work seamlessly with Bafang BBS01, BBS02, and BBSHD motors. It ensures a safe and efficient riding experience by cutting off power to the motor when either brake lever is activated.

  • Hydraulic brake compatibility: Designed to integrate with hydraulic braking systems for enhanced safety and control.
  • Power cut-off function: Instantly stops motor power when a brake lever is squeezed, preventing unintended acceleration and promoting rider safety.
  • Direct connection: Easily connects to Bafang BBS01, BBS02, and BBSHD motors for plug-and-play installation.

Specifications

This brake sensor cable is constructed with durable materials to withstand the rigors of e-bike use. It features a robust design and reliable connections for long-lasting performance.

Benefits

By installing this Ebike Hydraulic Brake Sensor Cable, you gain several crucial advantages:

  • Enhanced safety: The power cut-off feature immediately halts motor power during braking, reducing the risk of accidents and promoting rider confidence.
  • Improved control: Precise brake integration allows for smoother stopping and increased overall control over your e-bike.
  • Peace of mind: Knowing that your e-bike is equipped with a reliable safety feature provides added reassurance during every ride.

Usage

To use this brake sensor cable, simply connect it to the designated port on your Bafang BBS01, BBS02, or BBSHD motor and the hydraulic braking system. Ensure proper wiring connections according to the manufacturer's instructions for optimal performance.

This cable is designed to integrate seamlessly with existing e-bike setups, allowing you to enjoy enhanced safety and control without complex modifications.
description_da_auto:
Funktioner

Dette hydrauliske bremsesensorkabel til elcykler er specielt designet til at fungere problemfrit med Bafang BBS01-, BBS02- og BBSHD-motorer. Det sikrer en sikker og effektiv køreoplevelse ved at afbryde strømmen til motoren, når et af bremsegrebene aktiveres.

  • Kompatibilitet med hydrauliske bremser: Designet til at integrere med hydrauliske bremsesystemer for forbedret sikkerhed og kontrol.
  • Strømafbrydelsesfunktion: Stopper motorstrømmen øjeblikkeligt, når et bremsegreb klemmes, hvilket forhindrer utilsigtet acceleration og fremmer cyklistens sikkerhed.
  • Direkte tilslutning: Tilsluttes nemt til Bafang BBS01-, BBS02- og BBSHD-motorer til plug-and-play-installation.

Specifikationer

Dette bremsesensorkabel er konstrueret af holdbare materialer til at modstå påvirkningerne ved brug af elcykler. Den har et robust design og pålidelige forbindelser for langvarig ydeevne.

Fordele

Ved at installere dette hydrauliske bremsesensorkabel til elcykel opnår du flere afgørende fordele:

  • Forbedret sikkerhed: Strømafbrydelsesfunktionen stopper øjeblikkeligt motorens kraft under bremsning, hvilket reducerer risikoen for ulykker og fremmer cyklistens tillid.
  • Forbedret kontrol: Præcis bremseintegration giver mulighed for jævnere stop og øget generel kontrol over din elcykel.
  • Ro i sindet: At vide, at din elcykel er udstyret med en pålidelig sikkerhedsfunktion, giver ekstra tryghed under hver tur.

Brug

For at bruge dette bremsesensorkabel skal du blot tilslutte det til den angivne port på din Bafang BBS01-, BBS02- eller BBSHD-motor og det hydrauliske bremsesystem. Sørg for korrekt ledningsforbindelse i henhold til producentens anvisninger for optimal ydeevne.

Dette kabel er designet til problemfri integration med eksisterende elcykelopsætninger, så du kan nyde forbedret sikkerhed og kontrol uden komplekse ændringer.

titre: BAFANG Display DZ47 for M620 M600 M560 M510 M420 Mid Motors E-Bike Display Bike Computer with 0-9 PAS CAN Protocol
titre_da_auto: BAFANG Display DZ47 til M620 M600 M560 M510 M420 Mid Motors Elcykel Display Cykelcomputer med 0-9 PAS CAN Protokol
description:
Features

The BAFANG Display DZ47 is a versatile and user-friendly display designed specifically for BAFANG mid-drive motors, including the M620, M600, M560, M510, and M420 models. This sleek display offers a comprehensive range of features to enhance your e-bike riding experience.

  • LCD Display: The DZ47 features a clear and bright LCD screen that provides essential information at a glance, including speed, distance, battery level, assist mode, and more.
  • PAS Levels:
    • Provides customizable pedal assist levels (PAS) ranging from 0 to 9, allowing you to adjust the level of motor support based on your riding conditions and preferences.
  • CAN Protocol:
    • Utilizes the CAN protocol for seamless communication with compatible BAFANG motors, ensuring precise data transfer and accurate performance readings.

Specifications

The BAFANG Display DZ47 is engineered with precision to deliver reliable performance.

  • Display Type: LCD
  • PAS Levels: 0-9
  • Protocol: CAN
  • Compatibility: BAFANG M620, M600, M560, M510, and M420 Mid Motors

Benefits

The DZ47 offers numerous benefits that enhance your e-bike riding experience:

  • Enhanced Control: The customizable PAS levels allow you to precisely adjust the level of motor assistance for optimal control and efficiency.
  • Real-Time Information: The clear LCD display provides essential real-time data, empowering you to make informed riding decisions.
  • Seamless Integration: The CAN protocol ensures smooth and reliable communication between the display and your BAFANG motor.

Usage

The DZ47 is designed for easy installation and use.

To get started, simply connect the display to your compatible BAFANG mid-drive motor according to the manufacturer's instructions. Once connected, you can navigate through the menu options using the intuitive button controls to access various settings and display information.

  • LCD-display: DZ47 har en klar og lys LCD-skærm, der giver vigtige oplysninger med et hurtigt blik, herunder hastighed, distance, batteriniveau, assistancetilstand og mere.
  • PAS-niveauer:
    • Giver brugerdefinerede pedalassistanceniveauer (PAS) fra 0 til 9, så du kan justere niveauet af motorstøtte baseret på dine køreforhold og præferencer.
  • CAN-protokol:
    • Anvender CAN-protokollen til problemfri kommunikation med kompatible BAFANG-motorer, hvilket sikrer præcis dataoverførsel og nøjagtige ydelsesaflæsninger.

For at komme i gang skal du blot tilslutte skærmen til din kompatible BAFANG midterdrevsmotor i henhold til producentens instruktioner. Når den er tilsluttet, kan du navigere gennem menupunkterne ved hjælp af de intuitive knapper for at få adgang til forskellige indstillinger og displayoplysninger.

titre: For Bafang BBS01/BBS02 Mid Motor Chain Wheel Chainring 44T 46T 48T 52T Crank Arms Electric Bicycle Conversions 8FUN Parts
titre_da_auto: Til Bafang BBS01/BBS02 Midtermotor Kæde Hjul Kædering 44T 46T 48T 52T Krankarme Elcykel Konverteringer 8FUN Dele
description:
Features

This chain wheel crankset is designed specifically for Bafang BBS01 and BBS02 mid-drive electric bike motors. It's a direct replacement part, offering an upgrade path to customize your e-bike's gearing and performance.

  • Multiple Chainring Options: Choose from 44T, 46T, 48T, or 52T chainrings to perfectly match your riding style and terrain.
  • Durable Construction: Made with high-quality materials for long-lasting performance and reliability in demanding conditions.
  • Compatible with Bafang BBS01/BBS02 Motors: Ensures a seamless fit and integration with your existing motor system.

Specifications

The crankset features robust aluminum alloy crank arms with precise chainline alignment for efficient power transfer. The included chainring is compatible with standard single-speed drivetrains, offering a straightforward installation process.

  • Chainring Sizes: 44T, 46T, 48T, 52T
  • Crank Arm Material: Aluminum Alloy
  • Thread Type: Standard (refer to your motor's specifications)

Benefits

By upgrading your chain wheel and chainring, you can tailor your e-bike's gearing for optimal performance in various situations.

  • Increased Range: A larger chainring allows for more efficient pedaling at lower speeds, extending your electric bike's range on a single charge.
  • Improved Climbing Ability: Higher gear options provide the extra torque needed to conquer steep inclines with ease.
  • Enhanced Control: The precise gearing allows for better control over speed and acceleration in different riding conditions.

Usage

This chain wheel crankset is designed for installation on Bafang BBS01/BBS02 mid-drive electric bike motors. For proper installation, refer to your motor's manual or consult a qualified e-bike mechanic.
description_da_auto:

Dette kranksæt til kædehjul er designet specifikt til Bafang BBS01 og BBS02 elcykelmotorer med midterdrev. Det er en direkte reservedel, der tilbyder en opgraderingsmulighed for at tilpasse din elcykels gearing og ydeevne.

Kranksættet har robuste krumtaparme i aluminiumslegering med præcis kædelinjejustering for effektiv kraftoverførsel. Den medfølgende klinge er kompatibel med standard single-speed gearsystemer, hvilket giver en ligetil installationsproces.

  • Klingestørrelser: 44T, 46T, 48T, 52T

Fordele

Ved at opgradere dit klinge og klinge kan du skræddersy din elcykels gearing for optimal ydeevne i forskellige situationer.

  • Forbedret klatreevne:Højere gearmuligheder giver det ekstra drejningsmoment, der er nødvendigt for at klare stejle stigninger med lethed.
  • Forbedret kontrol: Den præcise gearing giver bedre kontrol over hastighed og acceleration under forskellige køreforhold.

Dette kranksæt er designet til montering på Bafang BBS01/BBS02 elcykelmotorer med midterdrev. For korrekt installation henvises til motorens manual eller kontaktes en kvalificeret elcykelmekaniker.

titre: Bafang 3.4inch eBike Display DPC020 CAN Display 5 PIN Male for Ebike Mid Drive Motor LCD Screen with USB Port 0-5 Modes
titre_da_auto: Bafang 3,4 tommer elcykeldisplay DPC020 CAN-display 5-bens hanstik til elcykel midterdrevsmotor LCD-skærm med USB-port 0-5 tilstande
description:
Features

The Bafang 3.4inch eBike Display DPC020 CAN Display is a sleek and intuitive display designed specifically for Bafang mid-drive eBike motors. With its bright, clear screen and user-friendly interface, this display provides all the essential information you need to enjoy a safe and efficient ride.

  • 3.4 inch Color LCD Screen: Provides a crisp and vibrant display for easy viewing of essential riding data.
  • CAN Bus Communication: Seamlessly integrates with Bafang mid-drive motors for accurate and real-time performance monitoring.
  • 5 Riding Modes: Customize your riding experience by selecting from various assistance levels to suit your needs.
  • USB Charging Port: Conveniently charge your mobile devices while on the go.
  • 5 PIN Male Connector: Ensures a secure and reliable connection with compatible Bafang motors.

Specifications

The Bafang DPC020 CAN Display is built to meet the demands of modern eBikes.

  • Display Size: 3.4 inches
  • Connection Type: 5 PIN Male
  • Display Resolution: High-resolution color LCD
  • Riding Modes: 5 adjustable levels of pedal assist
  • Additional Features: Integrated USB charging port

Benefits

The Bafang DPC020 CAN Display offers numerous benefits for eBike riders:

  • Enhanced Control and Visibility: Stay informed about your speed, battery level, distance traveled, and more with the clear LCD display.
  • Effortless Customization: Choose the riding mode that best suits your terrain and preferences.
  • Convenient Connectivity: Charge your mobile devices directly from the display using the built-in USB port.

Usage

The Bafang DPC020 CAN Display is designed to be user-friendly and easy to operate. Simply connect it to your compatible Bafang mid-drive motor using the 5 PIN male connector.

Navigate through the menus using the intuitive buttons on the display to adjust settings, select riding modes, and monitor your ride data. The USB charging port allows for convenient power access on the go.
description_da_auto:
Funktioner

Bafang 3,4-tommer eBike-displayet DPC020 CAN-displayet er et elegant og intuitivt display designet specielt til Bafang mid-drive eBike-motorer. Med sin klare, lyse skærm og brugervenlige grænseflade giver dette display alle de vigtige oplysninger, du har brug for, for at nyde en sikker og effektiv tur.

  • 3,4 tommer farve LCD-skærm: Giver en skarp og levende visning for nem visning af vigtige køredata.
  • CAN-buskommunikation: Integreres problemfrit med Bafang mid-drive-motorer for præcis og realtids præstationsovervågning.
  • 5 køretilstande: Tilpas din køreoplevelse ved at vælge mellem forskellige assistanceniveauer, der passer til dine behov.
  • USB-opladningsport: Oplad nemt dine mobile enheder, mens du er på farten.
  • 5-bens hanstik: Sikrer en sikker og pålidelig forbindelse med kompatible Bafang-motorer.

Specifikationer

Bafang DPC020 CAN-displayet er bygget til at opfylde kravene fra moderne elcykler.

  • Skærmstørrelse: 3,4 tommer
  • Forbindelsestype: 5-PIN han
  • Skærmopløsning: LCD-farveskærm med høj opløsning
  • Køretilstande: 5 justerbare niveauer af pedalassistance
  • Yderligere funktioner: Integreret USB-opladeport

Fordele

Bafang DPC020 CAN-skærmen tilbyder adskillige fordele for eBike-ryttere:

  • Forbedret kontrol og synlighed: Hold dig informeret om din hastighed, batteriniveau, tilbagelagt afstand og mere med det klare LCD-display.
  • Ubesværet tilpasning: Vælg den køretilstand, der passer bedst til dit terræn og dine præferencer.
  • Praktisk tilslutning: Oplad dine mobile enheder direkte fra skærmen ved hjælp af den indbyggede USB-port.

Brug

Bafang DPC020 CAN-skærmen er designet til at være brugervenlig og nem at betjene. Du skal blot tilslutte den til din kompatible Bafang-midtdrevsmotor ved hjælp af 5-bens hanstikket.

Naviger gennem menuerne ved hjælp af de intuitive knapper på skærmen for at justere indstillinger, vælge køretilstande og overvåge dine køredata. USB-opladningsporten giver nem adgang til strøm på farten.

titre: Bafang Display BN136 SW102 Display LCD Electric Bicycle Intelligent Instrument Display For Bafang Motor BBS01 BBS02 BBSHD
titre_da_auto: Bafang Display BN136 SW102 Display LCD Elcykel Intelligent Instrument Display Til Bafang Motor BBS01 BBS02 BBSHD
description:
Features

The Bafang Display BN136 SW102 is a smart and intuitive display designed specifically for Bafang electric bicycle motors, including the popular BBS01, BBS02, and BBSHD models. This LCD instrument panel offers a comprehensive range of features to enhance your riding experience and provide real-time information about your e-bike's performance.

  • Clear LCD Display: The BN136 features a bright and easy-to-read LCD screen that clearly displays vital data like speed, distance, battery level, and assist level.
  • Intuitive Controls:

    • Simple buttons allow you to effortlessly navigate menus and adjust settings on the fly.

  • Ride Data Monitoring:

    • Track your progress with comprehensive ride data such as total distance traveled, trip distance, and average speed.

Specifications

The Bafang Display BN136 SW102 is built to withstand the demands of e-biking.

  • Durable Construction: Designed with a robust construction for reliable performance in various riding conditions.
  • Water Resistance:

    • The display offers a level of water resistance, making it suitable for use in light rain or wet environments.

  • Compatible Motors:

    • Perfectly compatible with Bafang BBS01, BBS02, and BBSHD motor systems.

Benefits

This smart display elevates your e-biking experience by providing essential information at your fingertips. The BN136 SW102 empowers you to:

  • Ride Safely and Efficiently:

    • Monitor your speed, assist level, and battery status to make informed decisions for a safe and efficient ride.

  • Track Your Progress:

    • Analyze your ride data to monitor your fitness levels and identify areas for improvement.

  • Customize Your Ride:

    • Adjust settings like assist level and unit of measurement (km/h or mph) to personalize your e-bike experience.

Usage

The Bafang Display BN136 SW102 is seamlessly integrated with your Bafang motor. Simply follow the easy installation instructions provided with your display and connect it to your motor system.

Once installed, you'll have access to a clear LCD screen displaying all essential ride information. Use the intuitive buttons on the display to navigate menus, adjust settings, and customize your e-bike experience.

titre: Bicycle Stem Adjustable 90 Degree Road Mountain MTB Bike Table 105mm Rod Front Fork Stem for 25.4mm Handlebar Power Parts
titre_da_auto: Cykelfrempind Justerbar 90 Grader Landevej Mountain MTB Cykelbord 105mm Stang Forgaffel Frempind Til 25.4mm Styr Power Parts
description:
Features

This adjustable bicycle stem is designed to provide a secure and versatile connection between your handlebars and fork, enhancing your riding experience.

  • 90 Degree Rotation: The stem allows for a 90-degree rotation, giving you the flexibility to adjust your handlebar position for optimal comfort and control.
  • Adjustable Length: Fine-tune the reach of your handlebars with the adjustable length feature, tailoring it to your individual preferences and riding style.
  • Durable Construction: Crafted from robust materials, this stem is built to withstand the rigors of cycling on various terrains.
  • Compatible with 25.4mm Handlebar: Designed specifically for handlebars with a diameter of 25.4mm, ensuring a secure and snug fit.

Specifications

The Adjustable 90 Degree Road Mountain MTB Bike Stem features a 105mm rod length and is compatible with standard front forks and handlebars.

Benefits

This versatile stem offers numerous benefits to enhance your cycling experience:

  • Improved Comfort: Adjust the handlebar position for greater comfort, reducing strain on your wrists and back.
  • Enhanced Control: Fine-tune your reach and control over the bike for a more responsive and confident ride.
  • Versatility for Different Riding Styles: The adjustable features cater to various riding styles, from road cycling to mountain biking.

Usage

To install the stem, simply follow these steps:

  1. Align the stem with the front fork steerer tube.
  2. Securely tighten the stem bolts according to manufacturer instructions.
  3. Attach your handlebars to the stem and ensure a secure fit.

Remember to always consult your bicycle's manual for specific installation guidelines and torque specifications.
description_da_auto:
Funktioner

Denne justerbare cykelfrempind er designet til at give en sikker og alsidig forbindelse mellem dit styr og din forgaffel, hvilket forbedrer din køreoplevelse.

  • 90 graders rotation: Frempinden giver mulighed for en 90-graders rotation, hvilket giver dig fleksibiliteten til at justere din styrposition for optimal komfort og kontrol.
  • Justerbar længde: Finjuster styrets rækkevidde med den justerbare længdefunktion, og skræddersy den til dine individuelle præferencer og kørestil.
  • Holdbar konstruktion: Denne frempind er fremstillet af robuste materialer og er bygget til at modstå cyklingens påvirkninger i forskellige terræner.
  • Kompatibel med 25,4 mm styr: Designet specielt til styr med en diameter på 25,4 mm, hvilket sikrer en sikker og tæt pasform.

Specifikationer

Den justerbare 90 graders Road Mountain MTB-frempind har en stanglængde på 105 mm og er kompatibel med standard forgafler og styr.

Fordele

Denne alsidige frempind tilbyder adskillige fordele, der forbedrer din cykeloplevelse:

  • Forbedret komfort: Juster styrets position for større komfort, hvilket reducerer belastningen på dine håndled og ryg.
  • Forbedret kontrol: Finjuster din rækkevidde og kontrol over cyklen for en mere responsiv og selvsikker tur.
  • Alsidighed til forskellige kørestile: De justerbare funktioner passer til forskellige kørestile, fra landevejscykling til mountainbiking.

Brug

For at montere frempinden skal du blot følge disse trin:

  1. Juster frempinden med forgaffelens styrrør.
  2. Spænd frempindens bolte forsvarligt i henhold til producentens anvisninger.
  3. Fastgør dit styr til frempinden, og sørg for, at den sidder sikkert.

Husk altid at konsultere din cykels manual for specifikke installationsretningslinjer og momentspecifikationer.

titre: Bafang Mid Motor BBS01B BBS02B 48V 500W 750W 36V 250W Bicycle Motor Kit Electric Brushless Bike Motor Para Bicicleta for 68mm BB
titre_da_auto: Bafang Mid Motor BBS01B BBS02B 48V 500W 750W 36V 250W Cykelmotorsæt Elektrisk Børsteløs Cykelmotor til 68mm BB
description:
Features

The Bafang Mid Motor BBS01B/BBS02B offers a powerful and reliable electric bike conversion solution. Designed to seamlessly integrate with your bicycle, this motor kit delivers exhilarating performance and extended range.

  • Powerful Electric Drive: Available in various power outputs (36V 250W, 48V 500W, or 48V 750W), the Bafang BBS01B/BBS02B provides a substantial boost to your pedaling efforts.
  • Brushless Motor Technology: Experience smooth, quiet operation and increased efficiency thanks to the brushless motor design. This technology minimizes friction and maximizes power output.
  • Mid-Drive Placement: Strategically positioned within the bottom bracket (68mm BB shell), the mid-drive motor provides optimal weight distribution and enhances pedaling dynamics.
  • Versatile Installation: Designed for easy integration with a wide range of bicycles, this kit includes all necessary components for a successful conversion.

Specifications

The Bafang Mid Motor BBS01B/BBS02B boasts robust technical specifications to ensure reliable performance and durability:

  • Voltage Options: 36V or 48V
  • Power Outputs: 250W, 500W, or 750W
  • Bottom Bracket Shell Size: 68mm
  • Motor Type: Brushless

Benefits

By incorporating the Bafang Mid Motor BBS01B/BBS02B into your bicycle, you unlock a range of compelling benefits:

  • Effortless Riding: Conquer hills and long distances with ease, as the motor assists your pedaling efforts, reducing fatigue and enhancing your cycling experience.
  • Increased Range: Extend your riding range significantly by utilizing the electric assist, allowing you to explore further and enjoy longer adventures.
  • Improved Efficiency: The brushless motor technology delivers optimal energy efficiency, minimizing power consumption and extending battery life.

Usage

The Bafang Mid Motor BBS01B/BBS02B is designed for straightforward integration and operation:

Install the motor kit according to the provided instructions. Connect your chosen battery pack and control unit. Select your desired power level using the on-board display or controller. Pedal as usual, enjoying the seamless electric assist that boosts your pedaling force.
description_da_auto:
Funktioner

Bafang Mid Motor BBS01B/BBS02B tilbyder en kraftfuld og pålidelig løsning til konvertering af elektriske cykler. Dette motorsæt er designet til problemfri integration med din cykel og leverer spændende ydeevne og udvidet rækkevidde.

  • Kraftfuld elektrisk drivlinje: Bafang BBS01B/BBS02B fås i forskellige effektudgange (36V 250W, 48V 500W eller 48V 750W) og giver et betydeligt boost til din pedalering.
  • Børsteløs motorteknologi: Oplev jævn, stille drift og øget effektivitet takket være det børsteløse motordesign. Denne teknologi minimerer friktion og maksimerer effekt.
  • Placering af midterdrev:Strategisk placeret i krankboksen (68 mm krankboksskal) giver midterdrevsmotoren optimal vægtfordeling og forbedrer pedaldynamikken.
  • Alsidig installation:Dette sæt er designet til nem integration med en bred vifte af cykler og indeholder alle nødvendige komponenter til en vellykket konvertering.

Specifikationer

Bafang midtermotoren BBS01B/BBS02B kan prale af robuste tekniske specifikationer for at sikre pålidelig ydeevne og holdbarhed:

  • Spændingsmuligheder: 36V eller 48V
  • Effekter: 250W, 500W eller 750W
  • Krankboksskalstørrelse: 68 mm
  • Motortype: Børsteløs

Fordele

Ved at inkorporere Med Bafang Mid Motor BBS01B/BBS02B på din cykel får du en række overbevisende fordele:

  • Ubesværet kørsel:Bestem bakker og lange distancer med lethed, da motoren hjælper dig med at træde i pedalerne, reducerer træthed og forbedrer din cykeloplevelse.
  • Øget rækkevidde:Udvid din rækkevidde betydeligt ved at bruge den elektriske assistance, så du kan udforske længere og nyde længere eventyr.
  • Forbedret effektivitet:Den børsteløse motorteknologi leverer optimal energieffektivitet, minimerer strømforbruget og forlænger batteriets levetid.

Brug

Bafang Mid Motor BBS01B/BBS02B er designet til nem integration og betjening:

Installer motorsættet i henhold til de medfølgende instruktioner. Tilslut din valgte batteripakke og styreenhed. Vælg dit ønskede effektniveau ved hjælp af det indbyggede display eller controller. Træd i pedalerne som sædvanligt, og nyd den problemfri elektriske assistance, der øger din pedalkraft.

titre: BAFANG BBSHD Controller for 48V 1000W Mid Drive Motor with Front Lamp Connector and Gear Shift Sensor Connector
titre_da_auto: BAFANG BBSHD-controller til 48V 1000W mellemmotor med stik til forlygte og stik til gearskiftesensor
description:
Features

The BAFANG BBSHD Controller is designed to seamlessly integrate with your mid-drive electric bike system. This powerful controller delivers exceptional performance, enabling you to conquer hills and enjoy smooth rides.

  • 48V 1000W Output: Power through demanding terrain with ease.
  • Front Lamp Connector: Illuminate your path for enhanced visibility and safety at night.
  • Gear Shift Sensor Connector: Optimize power delivery based on your selected gear, ensuring efficient performance throughout your ride.

Specifications

This controller is engineered to meet the demands of high-performance e-bike systems.

  • Voltage: 48V
  • Power Output: 1000W
  • Connector Types: Front Lamp, Gear Shift Sensor

Benefits

The BAFANG BBSHD Controller offers a range of benefits for e-bike riders:

  • Increased Power and Performance: Enjoy effortless acceleration and climbing power with the 1000W output.
  • Enhanced Safety: The front lamp connector allows you to easily connect a headlight, improving visibility during nighttime riding.
  • Optimized Riding Experience: The gear shift sensor ensures that power delivery is tailored to your current gear selection, maximizing efficiency and performance.

Usage

This controller is designed for use with 48V mid-drive electric bike motors. It requires proper installation by a qualified technician to ensure safe and optimal operation.

Connect the front lamp and gear shift sensor cables according to the provided wiring diagram. Ensure all connections are secure and properly insulated.

  • Gearskiftesensorstik: Optimer strømforsyningen baseret på dit valgte gear, hvilket sikrer effektiv ydeevne under hele din tur.

  • Spænding: 48V

BAFANG BBSHD-controlleren tilbyder en række fordele for elcykelryttere:

  • Øget effekt og ydeevne: Nyd ubesværet acceleration og klatrekraft med 1000W-udgangen.

  • Optimeret køreoplevelse: Gearskiftesensoren sikrer, at effekttilførslen er skræddersyet til dit aktuelle gearvalg, hvilket maksimerer effektivitet og ydeevne.

description:
Features

This Wuxing Waterproof Brake Lever is designed specifically for Bafang BBS01B, BBS02B, and BBSHD mid-drive motor eBikes. It seamlessly integrates with your existing braking system to provide a safe and reliable cutoff power feature.

  • Waterproof Design: Withstands the elements and ensures consistent performance in various weather conditions.
  • Precise Braking Action: Delivers smooth and responsive braking control for enhanced safety.
  • Easy Installation: Designed for straightforward integration with your eBike's existing brake system.

Specifications

This product is designed to work seamlessly with Bafang BBS01B, BBS02B, and BBSHD mid-drive motor eBikes. It features a robust construction that can withstand the rigors of regular use.

Benefits

The Wuxing Waterproof Brake Lever offers several significant benefits for eBike riders:

  • Enhanced Safety: Automatically cuts power to the motor when the brakes are engaged, preventing unintended acceleration and enhancing overall safety.
  • Increased Control: Provides a reliable and responsive braking system for confident handling in various riding situations.
  • Weather Resistance: The waterproof design ensures consistent performance regardless of the weather conditions.

Usage

To use this brake lever, simply install it according to the provided instructions. When you apply the brakes, the motor power will automatically cut off. Release the brakes, and the motor will resume operation. This seamless integration ensures a safe and controlled riding experience.

description:
Features

The Bafang DPC010 Display is a comprehensive speedometer designed to seamlessly integrate with select Bafang mid-drive motors. This 4.0-inch screen offers a clear and intuitive interface, providing essential riding information at your fingertips.

  • Bluetooth Connectivity: Effortlessly connect your display to smartphones for advanced data tracking and customization options.
  • CAN Protocol Compatibility: Ensures smooth communication and data exchange with supported Bafang mid-drive motors, including the M620, M600, M560, M510, and M420 models.
  • Multi-Level Pedal Assist: Adjust your riding experience with 0-6 levels of pedal assist, tailoring power output to your needs and terrain.
  • Clear LCD Screen: The large 4.0-inch screen provides clear visibility of crucial data like speed, battery level, distance traveled, and more.

Specifications

The Bafang DPC010 Display offers a range of specifications designed for optimal performance and user experience:

  • Screen Size: 4.0 inches
  • Connectivity: Bluetooth
  • Protocol: CAN
  • Pedal Assist Levels: 0-6

Benefits

This display empowers riders with enhanced control, insights, and customization:

  • Real-Time Information: Stay informed about your speed, battery level, distance, and other vital data for safe and efficient riding.
  • Personalized Riding Experience: Customize your pedal assist levels to match your preferences and riding conditions.
  • Smartphone Integration: Access advanced features and data tracking through Bluetooth connectivity with compatible smartphones.
  • Seamless Motor Communication: The CAN protocol ensures smooth communication between the display and supported Bafang mid-drive motors.

Usage

Installing and using the Bafang DPC010 Display is straightforward. Simply connect it to your compatible Bafang mid-drive motor, following the provided instructions. The intuitive interface allows for easy navigation and access to essential information. Use the Bluetooth connection to sync with your smartphone for enhanced features and data analysis.

description:
Features

The Bafang DPC18 Electric Bike Display is a versatile and user-friendly solution designed to enhance your e-bike riding experience. This display seamlessly integrates with mid-drive motors, including the popular Bafang BBS01B, BBS02B, and BBSHD models.

  • Speedometer Functionality: Accurately tracks your speed in real-time, allowing you to monitor your progress and adjust your riding accordingly.
  • USB Charging Port: Conveniently charge your mobile devices directly from the display using the integrated USB port.
  • Mid-Drive Motor Compatibility: Specifically designed for compatibility with Bafang mid-drive motors, ensuring a seamless connection and data exchange.

Specifications

The Bafang DPC18 Electric Bike Display boasts several key specifications that contribute to its performance and usability:

  • Intuitive LCD Screen: Features a clear and easy-to-read LCD screen for displaying speed, battery level, and other essential information.
  • Durable Construction: Built with robust materials to withstand the rigors of outdoor riding conditions.
  • Sleek and Compact Design: Its streamlined design seamlessly integrates with your e-bike's handlebars, enhancing its aesthetic appeal.

Benefits

The Bafang DPC18 Electric Bike Display offers numerous benefits that elevate your riding experience:

  • Enhanced Safety: The speedometer function provides valuable speed awareness, contributing to safer riding practices.
  • Increased Convenience: The integrated USB charging port eliminates the need for separate charging cables, streamlining your rides.
  • Improved Performance Monitoring: Access real-time information about your speed and battery level, allowing for optimized riding performance.

Usage

Installing and using the Bafang DPC18 Electric Bike Display is straightforward:

1. Connect the display to your compatible Bafang mid-drive motor according to the provided instructions.

2. Power on the display by pressing the designated button.

3. Navigate through the menu options using the control buttons to adjust settings and view information such as speed, battery level, and odometer readings.

4. Utilize the USB charging port to conveniently charge your mobile devices while riding.
description_da_auto:

  • Speedometerfunktionalitet: Sporer præcist din hastighed i realtid, så du kan overvåge dine fremskridt og justere din kørsel i overensstemmelse hermed.
  • USB-opladningsport: Oplad dine mobile enheder nemt direkte fra displayet ved hjælp af den integrerede USB-port.
  • Kompatibilitet med centermotorer: Specifikt designet til kompatibilitet med Bafang centermotorer, hvilket sikrer en problemfri forbindelse og dataudveksling.

Specifikationer

Bafang DPC18 elcykeldisplayet kan prale af flere vigtige specifikationer, der bidrager til dets ydeevne og brugervenlighed:

  • Intuitiv LCD-skærm: Har en klar og letlæselig LCD-skærm til visning af hastighed, batteriniveau og andre vigtige oplysninger.
  • Holdbar konstruktion: Bygget med robuste materialer til at modstå de barske udendørs køreforhold.
  • Slank og kompakt design: Det strømlinede design integreres problemfrit med din elcykels styr, hvilket forbedrer dens æstetiske appel.

Fordele

Bafang DPC18 elektrisk cykeldisplay tilbyder adskillige fordele, der forbedrer din køreoplevelse:

  • Forbedret sikkerhed: Speedometerfunktionen giver værdifuld hastighedsbevidsthed, hvilket bidrager til mere sikker kørsel.
  • Øget bekvemmelighed: Den integrerede USB-opladerport eliminerer behovet for separate opladningskabler, hvilket strømliner dine ture.
  • Forbedret præstationsovervågning: Få adgang til information i realtid om din hastighed og batteriniveau, hvilket muliggør optimeret kørepræstation.

Brug

Installation og brug af Bafang DPC18 elektrisk cykeldisplay er ligetil:

4. Brug USB-opladeporten til nemt at oplade dine mobile enheder, mens du kører.

description:

titre: Bafang C965 LCD Display Speed Indicator Electric Bicycle Conversion Mid Motor Hub Motor BBS01B BBS02B 36V 48V 750W E-bike Kits
titre_da_auto: Bafang C965 LCD-display Hastighedsindikator Elcykel Konvertering Midtermotor Navmotor BBS01B BBS02B 36V 48V 750W Elcykelsæt
description:
Features

The Bafang C965 LCD Display is a powerful and versatile accessory designed to enhance your electric bicycle riding experience. This display seamlessly integrates with Bafang's popular BBS01B and BBS02B mid-drive motors, providing riders with essential information and control over their e-bike.

  • Speed Indicator: Clearly displays your current speed, allowing you to maintain a safe and efficient pace.
  • Battery Level Indicator: Monitors the remaining battery power, ensuring you know when it's time to recharge.
  • Cruise Control: Enable hands-free riding at a set speed for increased comfort on flat terrain.
  • Walk Assist Function: Provides assistance while walking your e-bike, making it easier to navigate crowded areas or hills.

Specifications

The Bafang C965 LCD Display is compatible with a range of voltage and wattage configurations:

  • Voltage: 36V or 48V
  • Wattage: 750W

Benefits

The Bafang C965 LCD Display offers numerous benefits to e-bike riders:

  • Enhanced Safety: The speed indicator and battery level monitoring features contribute to a safer riding experience.
  • Improved Comfort: Cruise control and walk assist functions reduce rider fatigue and effort.
  • Greater Control: Real-time data display allows for precise adjustment of riding parameters.

Usage

Installing the Bafang C965 LCD Display is relatively straightforward, typically involving connecting it to your Bafang BBS01B or BBS02B motor and wiring it to your bike's battery system. The display will then power on automatically when the system is activated. Refer to the manufacturer's instructions for detailed installation and operation guidelines.

With its intuitive interface and informative display, the Bafang C965 LCD Display empowers you to enjoy a safer, more efficient, and ultimately more enjoyable electric bicycle riding experience.
description_da_auto:
Funktioner

Bafang C965 LCD-displayet er et kraftfuldt og alsidigt tilbehør, der er designet til at forbedre din oplevelse på elcyklen. Displayet integreres problemfrit med Bafangs populære BBS01B- og BBS02B-centermotorer og giver rytterne vigtige oplysninger og kontrol over deres elcykel.

  • Hastighedsindikator: Viser tydeligt din aktuelle hastighed, så du kan opretholde et sikkert og effektivt tempo.
  • Batteriniveauindikator: Overvåger den resterende batteristrøm og sikrer, at du ved, hvornår det er tid til at genoplade.
  • Fartpilot: Muliggør håndfri kørsel med en indstillet hastighed for øget komfort i fladt terræn.
  • Gåhjælpsfunktion: Yder assistance, mens du går på din elcykel, hvilket gør det lettere at navigere i overfyldte områder eller bakker.

Specifikationer

Bafang C965 LCD-displayet er kompatibelt med en række spændings- og wattkonfigurationer:

  • Spænding: 36V eller 48V
  • Watt: 750W

Fordele

Bafang C965 LCD-displayet tilbyder adskillige fordele for elcykelryttere:

  • Forbedret sikkerhed: Hastighedsindikatoren og batteriniveauovervågningsfunktionerne bidrager til en mere sikker køreoplevelse.
  • Forbedret komfort: Fartpilot Kontrol- og ganghjælpefunktioner reducerer træthed og anstrengelse hos rytteren.
  • Større kontrol: Visning af data i realtid muliggør præcis justering af køreparametre.

Brug

Installation af Bafang C965 LCD-displayet er relativt ligetil og involverer typisk tilslutning til din Bafang BBS01B- eller BBS02B-motor og tilslutning af det til din cykels batterisystem. Displayet tænder derefter automatisk, når systemet aktiveres. Se producentens instruktioner for detaljerede installations- og betjeningsvejledninger.

Med sin intuitive brugerflade og informative display giver Bafang C965 LCD-displayet dig mulighed for at nyde en sikrere, mere effektiv og i sidste ende mere fornøjelig oplevelse med elektrisk cykel.

titre: Bafang 48V 750W BBS02B Electric Bicycle Conversion Kits 8fun M315 Mid Drive Motor Bike Fit for BB Size 68mm-73mm/100mm Engine
titre_da_auto: Bafang 48V 750W BBS02B elcykelkonverteringssæt 8fun M315 midterdrevsmotorcykel passer til krankboksstørrelse 68mm-73mm/100mm motor
description:
Features

The Bafang 48V 750W BBS02B Electric Bicycle Conversion Kit is a powerful and versatile system designed to transform your bicycle into an electric bike. It features an 8fun M315 mid-drive motor, known for its efficiency and smooth power delivery.

  • Mid-Drive Motor: The heart of the kit is the 8fun M315 mid-drive motor, which provides torque to the rear wheel through your bike's existing drivetrain. This placement offers superior weight distribution and efficient power transfer.
  • High Power Output: With a powerful 750W rating, this kit delivers ample assistance for tackling hills and navigating challenging terrain.
  • 48V System Voltage: The 48V system voltage ensures optimal performance and long-lasting battery life.
  • BB Size Compatibility: Designed to fit a wide range of bicycles, this kit is compatible with bottom bracket (BB) sizes ranging from 68mm to 73mm.

Specifications

The Bafang 45V 750W BBS02B Electric Bicycle Conversion Kit boasts several key specifications that contribute to its performance and reliability:

  • Motor Type: 8fun M315 Mid-Drive Motor
  • Power Output: 750W
  • Voltage: 48V
  • Bottom Bracket Size Compatibility: 68mm - 73mm, 100mm

Benefits

Converting your bicycle to an electric bike with the Bafang 48V 750W BBS02B kit offers numerous benefits:

  • Effortless Riding: The powerful motor assists you, making hills and long distances less strenuous.
  • Enhanced Range: Extend your cycling range significantly by relying on electric assistance when needed.
  • Improved Fitness: Use the pedal assist to customize your workout intensity and reach new fitness goals.
  • Eco-Friendly Transportation: Reduce your carbon footprint by choosing a more sustainable mode of transportation.

Usage

Installing this conversion kit involves replacing your existing bottom bracket with the included motor unit. The kit comes with comprehensive instructions and wiring diagrams to guide you through the process. The motor is controlled by a separate display unit (sold separately), allowing you to adjust assist levels, monitor battery life, and access other features.

Once installed, you can enjoy a new level of riding experience, effortlessly tackling challenging terrain and exploring further distances.
description_da_auto:
Funktioner

Bafang 48V 750W BBS02B elcykelkonverteringssæt er et kraftfuldt og alsidigt system designet til at forvandle din cykel til en elcykel. Det har en 8fun M315 midtermotor, der er kendt for sin effektivitet og jævne kraftoverførsel.

  • Midtermotor: Hjertet i sættet er 8fun M315 midtermotoren, som leverer drejningsmoment til baghjulet gennem din cykels eksisterende drivlinje. Denne placering giver overlegen vægtfordeling og effektiv kraftoverførsel.
  • Høj effekt: Med en kraftig 750W-klassificering leverer dette sæt rigelig assistance til at klare bakker og navigere i udfordrende terræn.
  • 48V systemspænding: 48V systemspændingen sikrer optimal ydeevne og lang batterilevetid.
  • Kompatibilitet med krankboksstørrelser: Dette sæt er designet til at passe til en bred vifte af cykler og er kompatibelt med krankboksstørrelser (BB) fra 68 mm til 73 mm.

Specifikationer

Bafang 45V 750W BBS02B elcykelkonverteringssæt kan prale af flere vigtige specifikationer, der bidrager til dets ydeevne og pålidelighed:

  • Motortype: 8fun M315 midterdrevsmotor
  • Effekt: 750W
  • Spænding: 48V
  • Kompatibilitet med krankboksstørrelser: 68 mm - 73 mm, 100 mm

Fordele

At konvertere din cykel til en elcykel med Bafang 48V 750W BBS02B-sættet tilbyder adskillige fordele:

  • Ubesværet kørsel: Den kraftfulde motor hjælper dig, hvilket gør bakker og lange distancer mindre anstrengende.
  • Forbedret rækkevidde: Forlæng din cykelrækkevidde betydeligt ved at bruge elektrisk assistance, når det er nødvendigt.
  • Forbedret kondition: Brug pedalassistancen til at tilpasse din træningsintensitet og nå nye fitnessmål.
  • Miljøvenlig transport: Reducer dit CO2-aftryk ved at vælge en mere bæredygtig transportform.

Brug

Installation af dette konverteringssæt indebærer at udskifte din eksisterende krankboks med den medfølgende motorenhed. Sættet leveres med omfattende instruktioner og ledningsdiagrammer, der guider dig gennem processen. Motoren styres af en separat displayenhed (sælges separat), så du kan justere assistanceniveauer, overvåge batterilevetiden og få adgang til andre funktioner.

Når den er installeret, kan du nyde et nyt niveau af cykeloplevelse, ubesværet tackle udfordrende terræn og udforske yderligere distancer.

titre: Bafang CAN 48V 500W Motor Brushless Mid Drive eBike Engine BBS02B BBS02 Electric Bicycle Conversion Kits 20Ah Lithium Battery
titre_da_auto: Bafang CAN 48V 500W Motor Børsteløs Midterdrev E-Bike Motor BBS02B BBS02 Elcykel Konverteringssæt 20Ah Lithium Batteri
description:
Features

The Bafang CAN 48V 500W Motor Brushless Mid Drive eBike Engine BBS02B is a powerful and versatile conversion kit designed to transform your bicycle into an electric bike. This mid-drive motor offers a smooth and natural riding experience, seamlessly blending with your pedaling power.

  • Brushless Motor: This type of motor delivers efficient power transfer and quiet operation, ensuring a comfortable ride.
  • CAN Interface: This interface allows for advanced communication between the motor, display, and battery, enabling precise control and performance monitoring.
  • Mid-Drive Placement: The motor is located in the middle of the bike, near the crankset. This placement provides optimal weight distribution and efficient power transfer to the pedals, mimicking a natural riding sensation.

Specifications

The Bafang CAN 48V 500W Motor Brushless Mid Drive eBike Engine BBS02B is built with robust specifications for reliable performance:

  • Voltage: 48V
  • Power Output: 500W
  • Display Compatibility: The motor supports compatible displays to provide riders with real-time information about speed, distance, battery level, and other essential data.
  • Battery Capacity: This kit includes a powerful 20Ah Lithium Battery, providing ample range for extended rides.

Benefits

Experience the numerous advantages of upgrading your bicycle with this conversion kit:

  • Effortless Pedaling: The 500W motor significantly reduces pedaling effort, making hills and long distances a breeze.
  • Increased Range: The high-capacity lithium battery provides extended range for your rides, allowing you to explore further without worrying about running out of power.
  • Improved Performance: Enjoy enhanced speed and acceleration capabilities, transforming your daily commute or leisure ride into an exciting experience.
  • Eco-Friendly Transportation: Reduce your carbon footprint by choosing a more sustainable mode of transportation.

Usage

This conversion kit is designed for easy installation on compatible bicycles. The comprehensive instruction manual guides you through the process, ensuring a smooth and successful conversion.

Once installed, simply select your desired assist level using the provided display controls and enjoy the convenience of electric-powered cycling. Remember to always follow local regulations and safety guidelines when operating an eBike.

Bafang CAN 48V 500W Motor Brushless Mid Drive eBike Engine BBS02B er et kraftfuldt og alsidigt konverteringssæt designet til at forvandle din cykel til en elcykel. Denne mid-drive motor tilbyder en jævn og naturlig køreoplevelse, der problemfrit blandes med din pedalkraft.

Bafang CAN 48V 500W Motor Brushless Mid Drive eBike Engine BBS02B er bygget med robuste specifikationer for pålidelig ydeevne:

This kit seamlessly integrates a robust brushless motor directly into your rear hub, delivering unmatched performance and efficiency.

titre: Ebike Display For Bafang 8FUN BBS01 BBS01B BBS02 BBS02B BBSHD 1000W 750W 500W 250W Mid Motor Ebike Parts with CAN Protocol
titre_da_auto: Elcykeldisplay til Bafang 8FUN BBS01 BBS01B BBS02 BBS02B BBSHD 1000W 750W 500W 250W midtermotor Elcykeldele med CAN-protokol
description:
Features

This ebike display is specifically designed to work seamlessly with Bafang 8FUN mid-drive motors, including the popular BBS01, BBS01B, BBS02, BBS02B, and BBSHD models. It features a user-friendly interface that provides all the essential information you need to control your ebike effectively.

  • CAN Protocol Support: Ensures smooth and reliable communication between the display and your Bafang motor for optimal performance.
  • Multiple Display Modes: Easily switch between various display modes to view information like speed, distance, battery level, assistance level, and more.
  • Intuitive Controls: Convenient buttons allow you to navigate through menus, adjust settings, and control your ebike's features with ease.

Specifications

This display is built to withstand the demands of ebike riding.

  • Compatible with a wide range of Bafang 8FUN motors (BBS01, BBS01B, BBS02, BBS02B, BBSHD) with varying power outputs (1000W, 750W, 500W, and 250W).
  • Durable construction designed to resist wear and tear.
  • Bright display for clear visibility in various lighting conditions.

Benefits

This ebike display enhances your riding experience by providing essential information and intuitive controls.

  • Real-Time Data: Stay informed about your speed, distance traveled, battery level, and assistance level for a more enjoyable and efficient ride.
  • Enhanced Control: Easily adjust settings and features to customize your riding experience to your preferences.
  • Improved Safety: Monitor your battery status and assist levels to ensure you have enough power throughout your ride.

Usage

Installation is straightforward, connecting directly to your Bafang 8FUN mid-drive motor. The user-friendly interface allows for easy navigation and adjustment of settings. Refer to the provided instructions for detailed installation and operation guidelines.
description_da_auto:
Funktioner

Dette elcykeldisplay er specielt designet til at fungere problemfrit med Bafang 8FUN centermotorer, herunder de populære BBS01-, BBS01B-, BBS02-, BBS02B- og BBSHD-modeller. Det har en brugervenlig grænseflade, der giver alle de vigtige oplysninger, du har brug for, for at styre din elcykel effektivt.

  • CAN-protokolunderstøttelse: Sikrer jævn og pålidelig kommunikation mellem displayet og din Bafang-motor for optimal ydeevne.
  • Flere displaytilstande: Skift nemt mellem forskellige displaytilstande for at se oplysninger som hastighed, afstand, batteriniveau, assistanceniveau og mere.
  • Intuitive kontroller: Praktiske knapper giver dig mulighed for nemt at navigere gennem menuer, justere indstillinger og styre din elcykels funktioner.

Specifikationer

Dette display er bygget til at modstå kravene ved elcykelkørsel.

  • Kompatibel med en bred vifte af Bafang 8FUN-motorer (BBS01, BBS01B, BBS02, BBS02B, BBSHD) med varierende effekt (1000W, 750W, 500W og 250W).
  • Holdbar konstruktion designet til at modstå slid.
  • Lysst display for klar synlighed under forskellige lysforhold.

Fordele

Dette elcykeldisplay forbedrer din køreoplevelse ved at give vigtige oplysninger og intuitive betjeningselementer.

  • Data i realtid: Hold dig informeret om din hastighed, tilbagelagte distance, batteriniveau og assistanceniveau for en mere behagelig og effektiv tur.
  • Forbedret kontrol: Juster nemt indstillinger og funktioner for at tilpasse din køreoplevelse til dine præferencer.
  • Forbedret sikkerhed: Overvåg din batteristatus og assistanceniveauer for at sikre, at du har nok strøm under hele din tur.

Brug

Installationen er ligetil og tilsluttes direkte til din Bafang 8FUN centermotor. Den brugervenlige grænseflade giver mulighed for nem navigation og justering af indstillinger. Se den medfølgende vejledning for detaljerede installations- og betjeningsvejledninger.

titre: Varstrom 125XV 48V 750W 500W Rear Hub Motor Kit 20 26 27.5 700C Electric Bicycle 16Ah 20Ah Cassette V Brake Bike Conversion Kit
titre_da_auto: Varstrom 125XV 48V 750W 500W Baghjulsnavmotorsæt 20 26 27,5 700C Elcykel 16Ah 20Ah Kassette V-bremse Cykelkonverteringssæt
description:
Features

The Varstrom 125XV E-Bike Conversion Kit is designed to seamlessly transform your traditional bicycle into a powerful electric ride. This comprehensive kit equips your bike with everything you need for an exhilarating e-bike experience.

  • Rear Hub Motor: A high-performance 750W rear hub motor provides ample power for effortless hill climbing and cruising at various speeds.
  • Battery Options: Choose from two convenient battery capacities: a 16Ah or a 20Ah lithium-ion battery pack, offering extended range for your rides.
  • Cassette Selection: A wide range cassette provides optimal gear ratios for diverse terrains and riding styles, ensuring smooth transitions between gears.
  • V-Brake System: Reliable V-brakes ensure safe and controlled stopping power in a variety of conditions.

Specifications

This kit is compatible with various wheel sizes and comes equipped with a 48V system for optimal performance.

  • Motor Power: 750W Peak, 500W Continuous
  • Voltage: 48V
  • Wheel Size Compatibility: 20", 26", 27.5", 700C
  • Battery Capacity Options: 16Ah or 20Ah

Benefits

By converting your existing bicycle, you gain a multitude of advantages:

  • Extended Range: Enjoy longer rides without the fatigue of pedaling solely.
  • Effortless Hill Climbing: Conquering steep inclines becomes a breeze with the powerful electric assist.
  • Increased Commuting Efficiency: Arrive at your destination refreshed and on time, even with challenging routes.

Usage

Installing the Varstrom 125XV E-Bike Conversion Kit is a relatively straightforward process that can be accomplished by following the provided instructions. This kit empowers you to personalize your cycling experience by adding electric assistance to any compatible bicycle, allowing for greater versatility and enjoyment on every ride.
description_da_auto:
Funktioner

Varstrom 125XV elcykelkonverteringssættet er designet til problemfrit at forvandle din traditionelle cykel til en kraftfuld elektrisk cykel. Dette omfattende sæt udstyrer din cykel med alt, hvad du behøver for en spændende elcykeloplevelse.

  • Baghjulsnavmotor: En højtydende 750W baghjulsnavmotor giver rigelig kraft til ubesværet bakkekørsel og cruising ved forskellige hastigheder.
  • Batterimuligheder: Vælg mellem to praktiske batterikapaciteter: en 16Ah eller en 20Ah lithium-ion batteripakke, der tilbyder udvidet rækkevidde til dine ture.
  • Kassetteudvalg: En kassette med bredt gearområde giver optimale gearforhold til forskellige terræner og kørestile, hvilket sikrer jævne overgange mellem gear.
  • V-bremsesystem: Pålidelige V-bremser sikrer sikker og kontrolleret bremsekraft under forskellige forhold.

Specifikationer

Dette sæt er kompatibelt med forskellige hjulstørrelser og er udstyret med et 48V-system for optimal ydeevne.

  • Motoreffekt: 750W Peak, 500W Continuous
  • Spænding: 48V
  • Hjulstørrelseskompatibilitet: 20", 26", 27,5", 700C
  • Batterikapacitetsmuligheder: 16Ah eller 20Ah

Fordele

Ved at konvertere din eksisterende cykel får du en lang række fordele:

  • Udvidet rækkevidde: Nyd længere ture uden trætheden ved udelukkende at træde i pedalerne.
  • Ubesværet bakkebestigning: Det bliver en leg at overvinde stejle stigninger med den kraftfulde elektriske assistance.
  • Øget pendlingseffektivitet: Ankom frisk og til tiden til din destination, selv på udfordrende ruter.

Brug

Installation af Varstrom 125XV E-Bike Conversion Kit er en relativt ligetil proces, der kan udføres ved at følge de medfølgende instruktioner. Dette sæt giver dig mulighed for at personliggøre din cykeloplevelse ved at tilføje elektrisk assistance til enhver kompatibel cykel, hvilket giver større alsidighed og nydelse på alle ride.

titre: Bafang G062 48V1000W Ebike Conversion Kit 26 Inch 20 Inch Rear Hub Motor Kits for 20/26 inch Snow Fat Bike Electronic Bike Kit
titre_da_auto: Bafang G062 48V1000W Ebike Konverteringssæt 26 tommer 20 tommer Baghjulsnavmotorsæt til 20/26 tommer Snow Fat Bike Elektronisk Cykelsæt
description:
Features

The Bafang G062 48V 1000W E-Bike Conversion Kit is designed to transform your existing 20 or 26 inch snow fat bike into a powerful and capable electric bike. This comprehensive kit includes everything you need for a seamless conversion, empowering you to tackle challenging terrain with ease.

  • Powerful Motor: The G062 features a robust 1000W rear hub motor, delivering exceptional torque and speed to conquer hills and navigate uneven surfaces.
  • Durable Construction: Designed for rugged use, the kit boasts a durable construction that can withstand demanding conditions.
  • Efficient Battery System: A 48V battery powers the system, providing ample energy for extended rides.
  • Smooth and Responsive Control: The Bafang G062 offers intuitive controls for effortless speed adjustment and precise power delivery.

Specifications

The Bafang G062 E-Bike Conversion Kit is specifically tailored to 20 or 26 inch snow fat bikes.

  • Voltage: 48V
  • Motor Wattage: 1000W
  • Wheel Size Compatibility: 20" & 26"
  • Drive System: Rear Hub Motor

Benefits

This conversion kit offers numerous benefits, transforming your snow fat bike into a versatile and enjoyable ride:

  • Effortless Hill Climbing: The powerful 1000W motor effortlessly conquers steep inclines, expanding your riding range.
  • Increased Riding Range: With its efficient battery system, enjoy extended rides without being tethered to a power source.
  • Enhanced Comfort and Convenience: Reduce strain on your legs and experience smoother rides, especially on challenging terrain.

Usage

To utilize the Bafang G062 Conversion Kit effectively:

  • Follow the provided installation instructions carefully to ensure a secure and proper fit.
  • Charge the battery fully before each ride.
  • Adjust the speed settings according to your comfort level and riding conditions.
  • Always wear appropriate safety gear, including a helmet, when operating an electric bike.
description_da_auto:
Funktioner

Bafang G062 48V 1000W elcykelkonverteringssættet er designet til at omdanne din eksisterende 20 eller 26 tommer snow fatbike til en kraftfuld og kapabel elcykel. Dette omfattende sæt indeholder alt, hvad du behøver for en problemfri konvertering, så du nemt kan tackle udfordrende terræn.

  • Kraftfuld motor: G062 har en robust 1000W baghjulsnavmotor, der leverer exceptionelt drejningsmoment og hastighed til at erobre bakker og navigere på ujævne overflader.
  • Holdbar konstruktion: Sættet er designet til robust brug og har en holdbar konstruktion, der kan modstå krævende forhold.
  • Effektivt batterisystem: Et 48V batteri driver systemet og giver rigelig energi til længere ture.
  • Jævn og responsiv kontrol: Bafang G062 tilbyder intuitive kontroller til ubesværet hastighedsjustering og præcis kraftlevering.

Specifikationer

Bafang G062 E-Bike Conversion Kit er specielt skræddersyet til 20 eller 26 tommer snow fatbikes.

  • Spænding: 48V
  • Motoreffekt: 1000W
  • Hjulstørrelseskompatibilitet: 20" & 26"
  • Drivsystem: Baghjulsnavmotor

Fordele

Dette konverteringssæt tilbyder adskillige fordele og forvandler din snow fatbike til en alsidig og fornøjelig cykel:

  • Ubesværet bakkebestigning: Den kraftfulde 1000W motor klarer ubesværet stejle stigninger og udvider din rækkevidde.
  • Øget rækkevidde: Med sit effektive batterisystem kan du nyde længere ture uden at være bundet til en strømkilde.
  • Forbedret komfort og bekvemmelighed: Reducer belastningen på dine ben og oplev mere jævne ture, især i udfordrende terræn.

Brug

Sådan bruger du Bafang G062 konverteringssættet effektivt:

  • Følg de medfølgende installationsvejledninger omhyggeligt for at sikre en sikker og korrekt montering.
  • Oplad batteriet helt før hver tur.
  • Juster hastighedsindstillingerne i henhold til dit komfortniveau og køreforholdene.
  • Bær altid passende sikkerhedsudstyr, inklusive en hjelm, når du betjener en elcykel.

titre_da_auto: SUTTO 36V 250W Navmotor Elcykel Sæt 26 27,5 28 29 700C Hjul Baghjul Elcykel Konverteringssæt 13Ah 17,4Ah 25Ah Batteri
description:
Features

The SUTTO 36V 250W Hub Motor Ebike Kit is your gateway to effortless cycling. This comprehensive kit provides everything you need to transform your existing bicycle into a powerful electric bike, opening up new possibilities for commuting, exploring trails, and enjoying leisurely rides.

  • Powerful 250W Hub Motor: Experience smooth and efficient acceleration with the integrated 250W hub motor, effortlessly tackling hills and maintaining speed on flat terrain.
  • Compatible Wheel Sizes:
    • This versatile kit fits a wide range of wheel sizes, including 26", 27.5", 28", and 29" as well as 700C wheels, ensuring compatibility with your current bicycle.
  • Rear Drive System:
    • The rear-wheel drive system delivers efficient power transfer to the ground, providing a responsive and stable riding experience.
  • Multiple Battery Options:
    • Choose from 13Ah, 17.4Ah, or 25Ah battery capacities to customize your range and riding needs. A larger battery capacity extends your ride time, allowing you to explore further.

Specifications

The SUTTO Ebike Kit is designed with high-quality components to ensure reliable performance and durability:

  • Motor Power: 250W
  • Voltage: 36V
  • Wheel Size Compatibility: 26", 27.5", 28", 29", and 700C
  • Drive System: Rear Hub Motor Drive
  • Battery Capacity Options: 13Ah, 17.4Ah, 25Ah

Benefits

Experience the numerous benefits of converting your bicycle into an electric bike with the SUTTO Ebike Kit:

  • Effortless Riding: Conquer hills and long distances with ease, thanks to the powerful motor assisting your pedaling.
  • Increased Range: Extend your cycling adventures with multiple battery options to choose from, allowing you to explore farther and longer.
  • Convenient Commuting:
    • Arrive at your destination feeling refreshed and energized, even after a long commute.
  • Eco-Friendly Choice:
    • Reduce your carbon footprint by choosing an electric bike over traditional vehicles for shorter trips.

Usage

Using the SUTTO Ebike Kit is simple and intuitive:

  • Install the motor, battery, and controller according to the provided instructions.
  • Connect the wiring harness and ensure all connections are secure.
  • Charge the battery using the included charger.
  • Turn on the e-bike system and select your desired power assist level.
  • Start pedaling and enjoy the smooth and effortless ride!
description_da_auto:
Funktioner

SUTTO 36V 250W Hub Motor Ebike Kit er din indgang til ubesværet cykling. Dette omfattende sæt indeholder alt, hvad du behøver for at forvandle din eksisterende cykel til en kraftfuld elcykel, hvilket åbner op for nye muligheder for pendling, udforskning af stier og afslappende ture.

  • Kraftfuld 250W navmotor: Oplev jævn og effektiv acceleration med den integrerede 250W navmotor, der ubesværet klarer bakker og holder hastigheden på fladt terræn.
  • Kompatible hjulstørrelser:
    • Dette alsidige sæt passer til en bred vifte af hjulstørrelser, herunder 26", 27,5", 28" og 29" samt 700C-hjul, hvilket sikrer kompatibilitet med din nuværende cykel.
  • Baghjulstræk:
    • Baghjulstrækket leverer effektiv kraftoverførsel til jorden, hvilket giver en responsiv og stabil køreoplevelse.
  • Flere batterimuligheder:
    • Vælg mellem batterikapaciteter på 13 Ah, 17,4 Ah eller 25 Ah for at tilpasse din rækkevidde og dine kørebehov. En større batterikapacitet forlænger din køretid, så du kan udforske mere.

Specifikationer

SUTTO Ebike Kit er designet med komponenter af høj kvalitet for at sikre pålidelig ydeevne og holdbarhed:

  • Motoreffekt: 250W
  • Spænding: 36V
  • Hjulstørrelseskompatibilitet: 26", 27,5", 28", 29", og 700C
  • Drivsystem: Baghjulsnavmotordrev
  • Batterikapacitetsmuligheder: 13Ah, 17,4Ah, 25Ah

Fordele

Oplev de mange fordele ved at omdanne din cykel til en elcykel med SUTTO Ebike Kit:

  • Ubesværet kørsel: Erobr bakker og lange afstande med lethed takket være den kraftfulde motor, der hjælper din pedalering.
  • Øget rækkevidde: Forlæng dine cykeleventyr med flere batterimuligheder at vælge imellem, så du kan udforske længere og længere.
  • Praktisk pendling:
    • Ankom til din destination forfrisket og energisk, selv efter en lang pendling.
  • Miljøvenligt valg:
    • Reducer dit CO2-aftryk ved at vælge en elcykel frem for traditionelle køretøjer til kortere ture.

Brug

Det er enkelt og intuitivt at bruge SUTTO Ebike Kit:

  • Installer motor, batteri og controller i henhold til den medfølgende vejledning.
  • Tilslut ledningsnettet, og sørg for, at alle forbindelser er sikre.
  • Oplad batteriet med den medfølgende oplader.
  • Tænd elcykelsystemet, og vælg det ønskede strømhjælpsniveau.
  • Begynd at pedalere, og nyd den jævne og ubesværede tur!

titre: Varstrom TSDZ16 1000W TSDZ8 750W TSDZ2B 500W 250W Mid Motor Kit Torque Sensor Bicycle Electric Bike Conversion Kit BB 68-73mm
titre_da_auto: Varstrom TSDZ16 1000W TSDZ8 750W TSDZ2B 500W 250W Midtermotorsæt Momentsensor Cykel Elcykel Konverteringssæt BB 68-73mm
description:
Features

The Varstrom TSDZ16, TSDZ8, TSDZ2B, and 250W mid motor conversion kits offer a powerful way to electrify your bicycle. These kits feature cutting-edge technology and design for an enhanced riding experience.

  • Mid Drive Motor: The centrally mounted motor provides excellent power transfer and efficiency, delivering smooth pedal assistance throughout your ride.
  • Torque Sensor: Precisely senses pedaling force to deliver proportional power, mimicking the feeling of natural pedaling.
  • Variety of Wattage Options: Choose from powerful 1000W, 750W, 500W, or 250W motors depending on your desired performance and riding conditions.
  • BB Shell Compatibility: Designed for a wide range of bicycles with bottom bracket (BB) shells measuring between 68mm and 73mm.

Specifications

The Varstrom TSDZ16, TSDZ8, TSDZ2B, and 250W mid motor kits are built with robust components to ensure reliable performance.

  • Motor Types: TSDZ16 (1000W), TSDZ8 (750W), TSDZ2B (500W), 250W
  • Bottom Bracket Shell Size: 68mm - 73mm

Benefits

Elevate your cycling experience with the Varstrom mid motor kits.

  • Increased Power & Range: Conquer hills effortlessly and extend your riding distance.
  • Reduced Physical Strain: Enjoy effortless rides, making longer journeys more comfortable.
  • Eco-Friendly Transportation: Choose a sustainable alternative to gasoline-powered vehicles.

Usage

Installing the Varstrom TSDZ16, TSDZ8, TSDZ2B, and 250W kits is relatively straightforward. The kit typically includes all necessary components and detailed instructions for a smooth installation process.

Once installed, you can seamlessly integrate the motor into your existing bicycle setup. The torque sensor will automatically adjust the power output based on your pedaling effort, providing a natural and responsive riding experience.

  • Midtermotor: Den centralt monterede motor giver fremragende kraftoverførsel og effektivitet og leverer jævn pedalassistance under hele din tur.
  • Momentsensor: Registrerer præcist pedalkraften for at levere proportional kraft, der efterligner følelsen af ​​naturlig pedalering.
  • Forskellige watt-muligheder: Vælg mellem kraftfulde 1000W, 750W, 500W eller 250W motorer afhængigt af din ønskede ydeevne og køreforhold.
  • Kompatibilitet med krankboksskaller: Designet til en bred vifte af cykler med krankboksskaller, der måler mellem 68 mm og 73 mm.

Specifikationer

Varstrom TSDZ16, TSDZ8, TSDZ2B og 250W mellemmotorsæt er bygget med robuste komponenter for at sikre pålidelig ydeevne.

  • Motortyper: TSDZ16 (1000W), TSDZ8 (750W), TSDZ2B (500W), 250W
  • Krankboksstørrelse: 68 mm - 73 mm

Fordele

Giv din cykeloplevelse et bedre look med Varstrom mid-motor-kittene.

  • Øget effekt og rækkevidde: Kør ubesværet op ad bakker og forlæng din køredistance.
  • Reduceret fysisk belastning: Nyd ubesværede ture, der gør længere ture mere behagelige.
  • Miljøvenlig transport: Vælg et bæredygtigt alternativ til benzindrevne køretøjer.

Brug

Det er relativt ligetil at installere Varstrom TSDZ16-, TSDZ8-, TSDZ2B- og 250W-kittene. Sættet indeholder typisk alle nødvendige komponenter og detaljerede instruktioner for en problemfri installationsproces.

Når motoren er installeret, kan du problemfrit integrere den i din eksisterende cykelopsætning. Momentsensoren justerer automatisk effekten baseret på din pedalindsats, hvilket giver en naturlig og responsiv køreoplevelse.
