description:
Features

This Gear Shift Sensor is designed specifically for Bafang BBS01/02B and BBSHD mid-drive electric bike systems. It seamlessly integrates with your existing setup, ensuring accurate gear position detection for optimal performance.

  • Compatible with 3-pin shift cables
  • Precisely detects gear changes for smooth power delivery
  • Enhances riding experience by providing responsive and accurate assistance

Specifications

This Gear Shift Sensor is engineered to meet the demands of electric bike systems. It features robust construction and reliable performance.

  • Compatible with Bafang BBS01/02B and BBSHD motors
  • Utilizes a 3-pin connector for secure and stable connection

Benefits

By incorporating this Gear Shift Sensor into your electric bike setup, you unlock several key benefits:

  • Improved Riding Experience: Precise gear detection ensures seamless power transfer, providing a smoother and more responsive ride.
  • Optimized Performance: The sensor accurately communicates with the motor to deliver appropriate assistance based on your chosen gear, maximizing efficiency and power output.
  • Enhanced Safety: Accurate gear sensing contributes to safer riding by ensuring the motor's output aligns with your current gear selection.

Usage

Installing this Gear Shift Sensor is straightforward. Connect the sensor to the 3-pin connector on your Bafang BBS01/02B or BBSHD motor and ensure it is securely attached to the shift cable mechanism. After installation, calibrate the sensor according to the instructions provided with your electric bike system.

This Gear Shift Sensor plays a vital role in ensuring optimal performance and safety for your Bafang mid-drive electric bike. By accurately detecting gear changes, it allows for smooth power delivery and enhances your overall riding experience.

  • Bruger et 3-bens stik til sikker og stabil forbindelse

Fordele

description:
Features

The Bafang 750W 48V Motor Kit is a comprehensive solution for converting your bicycle into an electric bike. Designed with power and performance in mind, this kit features the robust Bafang BBS02 or BBS02B motor, known for its durability and exceptional torque output. The central drive location ensures optimal weight distribution and a natural riding experience.

  • 750W High-Power Motor: Experience exhilarating acceleration and effortless uphill climbs with the powerful 750W motor.
  • 48V System Voltage: Optimized for efficiency and performance, delivering ample power throughout your rides.
  • BBS02 or BBS02B Motor Option: Choose between the highly reliable and efficient BBS02 or the advanced BBS02B motor with integrated display functionality.
  • Central Drive Placement: Provides balanced weight distribution for a natural and responsive riding experience.

Specifications

This Bafang motor kit utilizes proven components to deliver a reliable and efficient electric biking experience.

  • Motor Type: Brushless geared hub
  • Voltage: 48V
  • Power Output: 750W
  • Maximum Torque: High torque output for effortless climbing and acceleration
  • Chainring Compatibility: Wide range of chainring options available to customize your gearing

Benefits

Transform your bicycle into a powerful electric bike and enjoy numerous benefits:

  • Effortless Commuting: Conquer hills and long distances with ease, making your daily commute more enjoyable.
  • Increased Range: The 48V system and efficient motor provide extended range for longer adventures.
  • Enhanced Performance: Experience exhilarating acceleration and top speeds to make every ride exciting.
  • Reduced Physical Strain: Pedal less and enjoy a comfortable ride, ideal for riders of all fitness levels.

Usage

Installing this Bafang motor kit requires some mechanical knowledge and tools. It involves replacing your existing crankset with the provided Bafang motor assembly. Detailed instructions are included to guide you through the installation process. Proper wiring and connection to a compatible battery pack are essential for safe and successful operation.

Once installed, the system can be controlled via a separate display (for BBS02B) or by using a thumb throttle. The Bafang 750W motor kit offers several assistance modes, allowing you to customize your pedaling effort based on your needs and preferences.

Specifications

The Varstrom Tongsheng TSDZ series boasts several key specifications:

  • Battery Capacity: 13Ah or 20Ah (depending on model)

Benefits

These mid-drive motor kits offer numerous benefits for cyclists:

  • Increased Pedaling Efficiency: The powerful motor assists your pedaling, making hills and long distances easier to conquer.
  • Enhanced Riding Experience: The torque sensor provides smooth and natural power delivery, mimicking the feeling of traditional cycling.
  • Extended Range: Choose from 13Ah or 20Ah battery options for longer rides without needing to recharge frequently.
  • Eco-Friendly Transportation: Reduce your carbon footprint by opting for an electric bike powered by a rechargeable battery.

Usage

The Varstrom Tongsheng TSDZ16, TSDZ8, and TSDZ2B kits are designed to be easily installed on various bicycles. Following the provided instructions, you can seamlessly integrate the motor, battery, and controller into your bike's frame. Once installed, simply pedal as usual, and the motor will provide assistance based on your pedaling force.

These kits are ideal for commuters, recreational riders, and anyone seeking a more efficient and enjoyable cycling experience.

The Bafang BBS02B Mid Drive Motor Bike Conversion Kit provides a powerful and efficient way to electrify your bicycle. This kit features a robust mid-drive motor, designed for optimal torque and performance, making hills and long rides a breeze.

  • Powerful 500W Motor: Experience effortless acceleration and conquer steep inclines with ease.
  • 36V System Voltage: Provides ample power for a smooth and enjoyable riding experience.
  • 8Fun M315 Cassete: Enjoy seamless gear shifting for optimal performance in various terrains.
  • Fits BB Size 68mm-73mm: Compatible with a wide range of bicycle frames.
  • 44T Chainring: Offers efficient power transfer from the motor to the pedals.

Specifications

This Bafang conversion kit is built with high-quality components, ensuring reliable performance and durability:

  • Motor Type: Mid-Drive
  • Power Output: 500W
  • Voltage: 36V
  • Cassette Compatibility: 8Fun M315
  • Bottom Bracket Size: 68mm-73mm
  • Chainring: 44T

Benefits

Transform your bicycle into an electric marvel with the Bafang BBS02B Conversion Kit:

  • Effortless Cycling: Conquer hills and distances with ease, making cycling more enjoyable for everyone.
  • Enhanced Range and Efficiency: Extend your ride time and reduce fatigue by utilizing the motor's assistance.
  • Environmentally Friendly: Reduce your carbon footprint by opting for an electric-assisted bicycle.

Usage

The Bafang BBS02B Conversion Kit is designed to be user-friendly. After installation, simply adjust the assistance level using the controller (sold separately), and enjoy the benefits of an electric bike. This kit is perfect for individuals who want to upgrade their existing bicycles with a powerful and reliable mid-drive motor system.
description_da_auto:
Funktioner

Bafang BBS02B midterdrevskonverteringssættet til motorcykel giver en kraftfuld og effektiv måde at elektrificere din cykel på. Dette sæt har en robust midterdrevsmotor, designet til optimalt drejningsmoment og ydeevne, hvilket gør bakker og lange ture til en leg.

  • Kraftfuld 500W motor: Oplev ubesværet acceleration og overvind stejle stigninger med lethed.
  • 36V systemspænding: Giver rigelig kraft til en jævn og behagelig køreoplevelse.
  • 8Fun M315 kassette: Nyd problemfri gearskift for optimal ydeevne i forskellige terræner.
  • Passer til krankboksstørrelse 68mm-73mm: Kompatibel med en bred vifte af cykelstel.
  • 44T klinge: Giver effektiv kraftoverførsel fra motoren til pedalerne.

Specifikationer

Dette Bafang-konverteringssæt er bygget med komponenter af høj kvalitet, hvilket sikrer pålidelig ydeevne og holdbarhed:

  • Motortype: Midterdrev
  • Effekt: 500W
  • Spænding: 36V
  • Kassette Kompatibilitet: 8Fun M315
  • Krankboksstørrelse: 68 mm-73 mm
  • Kædering: 44T

Fordele

Forvandl din cykel til et elektrisk vidunder med Bafang BBS02B konverteringssættet:

  • Ubesværet cykling: Erobr bakker og distancer med lethed, hvilket gør cykling mere behageligt for alle.
  • Forbedret rækkevidde og effektivitet: Forlæng din cykeltid og reducer træthed ved at bruge motorens assistance.
  • Miljøvenlig: Reducer dit CO2-aftryk ved at vælge en elektrisk cykel.

Brug

Bafang BBS02B konverteringssættet er designet til at være brugervenligt. Efter installationen skal du blot justere assistanceniveauet ved hjælp af controlleren (sælges separat) og nyde fordelene ved en elektrisk cykel. Dette sæt er perfekt til personer, der ønsker at opgradere deres eksisterende cykler med et kraftfuldt og pålideligt mellemmotorsystem.

titre: BAFANG BBSHD 1000W 52V 48V Kit Ebike Conversion Kit Mid Drive Motor 8FUN M615 Electric Bicycle Engine 68mm/100mm/120mm CAN Bus
titre_da_auto: BAFANG BBSHD 1000W 52V 48V Sæt Elcykel Konverteringssæt Midterdrevsmotor 8FUN M615 Elcykelmotor 68mm/100mm/120mm CAN Bus
description:
Features

The BAFANG BBSHD 1000W 52V 48V Ebike Conversion Kit is a powerful and versatile mid-drive motor designed to transform your bicycle into an electric one. This kit features the renowned 8FUN M615 engine, known for its robust construction and exceptional performance.

  • Powerful 1000W Motor: Experience exhilarating acceleration and effortless hill climbing with the high-torque 1000W motor.
  • Dual Voltage Compatibility (52V & 48V):
    • Adapt to different battery configurations for optimal performance.
  • Mid-Drive Design: Located in the center of your bike, this motor provides a natural and efficient riding experience.
  • CAN Bus Communication:
    • Enables seamless communication between the motor, controller, and display for smooth operation.
  • Multiple Crankshaft Options (68mm/100mm/120mm):
    • Customize the installation to perfectly fit your bicycle frame.

Specifications

This powerful conversion kit offers a range of specifications designed for performance and reliability:

  • Motor Power: 1000W
  • Voltage Options: 48V or 52V
  • Shaft Diameter Options: 68mm, 100mm, 120mm
  • Communication Protocol: CAN Bus

Benefits

The BAFANG BBSHD Ebike Conversion Kit offers a multitude of benefits for cyclists seeking an enhanced riding experience:

  • Effortless Hill Climbing: Conquer steep inclines with ease thanks to the powerful motor.
  • Increased Range and Efficiency:
    • Extend your rides and conserve energy by using electric assistance.
  • Enhanced Speed and Acceleration:
    • Enjoy faster acceleration and reach higher speeds for a more exhilarating ride.
  • Versatile Compatibility:
    • Adapt to different battery systems and choose the perfect crankshaft length for your bike.

Usage

This conversion kit is designed for experienced cyclists who are comfortable with bicycle mechanics. Installation requires some technical knowledge and tools. Refer to the detailed instructions provided with the kit for a step-by-step guide.

titre: Bafang Rear Hub Motor 48V 1000W G062.1000 DC Electric Bike Conversion Kit With Disc Brake For 20/26 inch Fat Bike Electronic Kit
titre_da_auto: Bafang baghjulsnavmotor 48V 1000W G062.1000 DC elcykelkonverteringssæt med skivebremse til 20/26 tommer fatbike elektronisk sæt
description:
Features

The Bafang G062.1000 Rear Hub Motor is a powerful and versatile electric bike conversion kit designed for fat bikes with 20-inch or 26-inch wheels. It features a robust hub motor that delivers impressive torque, enabling you to conquer challenging terrains with ease.

  • High-Performance 1000W Motor: Experience exceptional power and acceleration for demanding riding conditions.
  • Durable Rear Hub Design: The rear hub motor is specifically engineered for fat bikes, providing reliable performance and durability.
  • Integrated Disc Brake System: Enjoy enhanced safety and control with the integrated disc brake system, allowing for smooth and efficient braking.

Specifications

This electric bike conversion kit is built to deliver exceptional performance and reliability.

  • Voltage: 48V
  • Motor Wattage: 1000W
  • Wheel Size Compatibility: 20-inch or 26-inch Fat Bikes

Benefits

Transform your fat bike into an electric powerhouse with the Bafang G062.1000 conversion kit.

  • Effortless Riding: Conquer hills and long distances with ease, thanks to the powerful motor assistance.
  • Enhanced Performance: Experience increased speed and acceleration for a more thrilling riding experience.
  • Improved Safety: The integrated disc brake system provides reliable stopping power for added safety on various terrains.

Usage

This electric bike conversion kit is designed to be easily installed by experienced bicycle mechanics.

It requires a compatible battery and controller, which are sold separately. After installation, the system can be controlled via a handlebar display, allowing you to adjust motor assistance levels and monitor battery status.
